{"title":"Linux最快部署clash代理","slug":"2026-4-29","date":"2026-04-28T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2026-04-29T07:19:44.112Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2026-4-29.json","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://unpkg.com/volantis-static@0.0.1654736714924/media/org.volantis/logo/256/safari.png","https://bu.dusays.com/2026/04/29/69f19b1652a99.png","https://bu.dusays.com/2026/04/29/69f19c63db5ca.png"],"content":"<h2 id=\"1-先决条件\"><a href=\"#1-先决条件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1 先决条件\"></a>1 先决条件</h2><ul>\n<li>主流Linux发行版</li>\n<li>mihomo内核</li>\n<li>完全命令行操作</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tag link\"><a class=\"link-card\" title=\"项目地址\" href=\"https://github.com/nelvko/clash-for-linux-install/\"><div class=\"left\"><img src=\"https://unpkg.com/volantis-static@0.0.1654736714924/media/org.volantis/logo/256/safari.png\" class=\"lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https://unpkg.com/volantis-static@0.0.1654736714924/media/org.volantis/logo/256/safari.png\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/></div><div class=\"right\"><p class=\"text\">项目地址</p><p class=\"url\">https://github.com/nelvko/clash-for-linux-install/</p></div></a></div>\n\n<h2 id=\"2-安装\"><a href=\"#2-安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2 安装\"></a>2 安装</h2><ol>\n<li>使用加速前缀拉取项目</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git <span class=\"built_in\">clone</span> --branch master --depth 1 https://gh-proxy.org/https://github.com/nelvko/clash-for-linux-install.git \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &amp;&amp; <span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> clash-for-linux-install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>自定义具体配置，不通过默认 subconverter 进行本地订阅转换</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li><p>复制本地配置信息<br><img src=\"https://bu.dusays.com/2026/04/29/69f19b1652a99.png\" class=\"lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https://bu.dusays.com/2026/04/29/69f19b1652a99.png\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" alt=\"复制本地配置信息\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>粘贴信息到 <code>config.yaml</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nano ./resources/config.yaml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://bu.dusays.com/2026/04/29/69f19c63db5ca.png\" class=\"lazyload\" data-srcset=\"https://bu.dusays.com/2026/04/29/69f19c63db5ca.png\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" alt=\"粘贴到配置\"></p>\n<p>这一步主要是现在很多机场的订阅都不能通过subconverter正常转换，会丢失节点等，麻烦又闹心，从 Windows 的 Clash Verge 直接复制配置，简单直接。要是机场配置支持subconverter转换，可以跳过这一步，下一步会自动引导输入url。</p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>安装脚本落地为常驻服务。</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">bash install.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"3-常用命令\"><a href=\"#3-常用命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3 常用命令\"></a>3 常用命令</h2><ol>\n<li>优雅启停</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ clashon</span><br><span class=\"line\">😼 已开启代理环境</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ clashoff</span><br><span class=\"line\">😼 已关闭代理环境</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Web 控制台</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ clashui</span><br><span class=\"line\">╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════╗</span><br><span class=\"line\">║                😼 Web 控制台                  ║</span><br><span class=\"line\">║═══════════════════════════════════════════════║</span><br><span class=\"line\">║                                               ║</span><br><span class=\"line\">║     🔓 注意放行端口：9090                      ║</span><br><span class=\"line\">║     🏠 内网：http://192.168.0.1:9090/ui       ║</span><br><span class=\"line\">║     🌏 公网：http://8.8.8.8:9090/ui           ║</span><br><span class=\"line\">║     ☁️ 公共：http://board.zash.run.place      ║</span><br><span class=\"line\">║                                               ║</span><br><span class=\"line\">╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════╝</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ clashsecret mysecret</span><br><span class=\"line\">😼 密钥更新成功，已重启生效</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ clashsecret</span><br><span class=\"line\">😼 当前密钥：mysecret</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","more":"<h2 id=\"1-先决条件\"><a href=\"#1-先决条件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1 先决条件\"></a>1 先决条件</h2><ul>\n<li>主流Linux发行版</li>\n<li>mihomo内核</li>\n<li>完全命令行操作</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tag link\"><a class=\"link-card\" title=\"项目地址\" href=\"https://github.com/nelvko/clash-for-linux-install/\"><div class=\"left\"><img src=\"https://unpkg.com/volantis-static@0.0.1654736714924/media/org.volantis/logo/256/safar